===Noun===
'''Argentite''' (''[[uncountable]]''), ''Mineralogy''

# A [[primary ore]] of [[silver]], found in [[vein]]s with native silver.

*'''Composition:''' [[Silver]] [[sulphide]], <math>Ag_2S</math>

*'''Habit:''' [[Crystal]]s are [[cubic]] or [[hexoctahedral]], but usually distorted and difficult to recognize.

*'''Physical properties:''' Hardness 2-2.5; Specific gravity 7.3; Luster metallic, usually tarnished dull black; Color lead gray on fresh surfaces. Sectile (can be cut with a knife).

